{#- Icon rendered before a page's h1.
    Set `icon` (and optionally `iconWeight`) in the page's front matter.
    Falls back to the defaults in _data/metadata.js.
    Two icons are rendered stacked: the base weight (duotone by default) and a
    `fill` version that cross-fades in on hover — see `.h1-icon` in index.css. -#}
{%- set iconName = icon or metadata.icon.name -%}
{%- set iconWeightResolved = iconWeight or metadata.icon.weight -%}
{%- set iconSize = iconSize or metadata.icon.size or 40 -%}
{%- if iconName -%}
<span class="h1-icon">{% phosphor iconName, iconSize, iconWeightResolved %}{% phosphor iconName, iconSize, "fill" %}</span>
{%- endif -%}
